<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:14:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“措施升级”：内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的分歧在人质谈判中达到顶峰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/an-escalation-of-measures-netanyahu-gallants-rift-peaks-amid-hostage-talks/00000190-bf84-de8b-adfc-bfa43d5a0000</link><description>即使是内塔尼亚胡联盟中最极右翼的成员也认为他的政策只是另一个伎俩，旨在挫败任何协议。官员们认为，如果内塔尼亚胡确实挫败了这笔交易，加兰特将再次面对公众对他发出警告</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/an-escalation-of-measures-netanyahu-gallants-rift-peaks-amid-hostage-talks/00000190-bf84-de8b-adfc-bfa43d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道内塔尼亚胡称人质“遭受痛苦，但没有死亡”，家人要求澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/hostage-families-want-answers-after-pm-reportedly-says-theyre-suffering-not-dying/00000190-c05e-d211-a5da-ed5fd8350000</link><description>人质家庭论坛总部表示，内塔尼亚胡的言论“事实上不准确，而且非常不负责任”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:34:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/hostage-families-want-answers-after-pm-reportedly-says-theyre-suffering-not-dying/00000190-c05e-d211-a5da-ed5fd8350000</guid></item><item><title>经过九个月的战争后，哈马斯在加沙内外有多受欢迎？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-popular-is-hamas-in-gaza-and-outside-of-it-after-nine-months-of-war/00000190-bfda-d211-a5da-ffdbea210000</link><description>最近的民意调查结果各不相同，但在支持哈马斯及其代表的一切方面，它们显示加沙人和约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人之间的差距不断扩大。尽管那些遭受战争后果的人基本上都幻灭了，但其他地方的巴勒斯坦人仍然对哈马斯持积极态度。可能是因为“同情是免费的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-popular-is-hamas-in-gaza-and-outside-of-it-after-nine-months-of-war/00000190-bfda-d211-a5da-ffdbea210000</guid></item><item><title>“这让我很惊讶，我不知道”：内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日以色列军事基地发生的事情感到“惊讶”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</link><description>第 12 频道新闻播出了内塔尼亚胡与在纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所被杀的以色列国防军女观察员家属会面的录音，显示总理不知道这些士兵没有携带武器，而且官员们探望了这些家庭</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部发现六岁儿童尸体，母亲涉嫌谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</link><description>在尸体被发现之前，一名33岁的女子在荷兹利亚购物中心入口处用斧头袭击一名保安并轻伤了他，随后被捕。警方怀疑她是男孩的母亲，并且她患有精神疾病</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队向极端正统派男子发出数千份征兵通知，引发抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</link><description>以色列军队预计将向正在犹太学院工作或已经退学的极端正统派男子发出约 6,000 份征兵通知。军队宣布这一消息后，大约 150 名来自极端极端正统教派的男子封锁了一条高速公路以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</guid></item><item><title>人权观察：至少五个巴勒斯坦组织在10月7日的袭击中犯有战争罪和反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</link><description>该组织的新报告反驳了哈马斯的说法，即其战斗人员被指示不要伤害儿童、妇女和老人，并指出对平民的杀害是有系统、有预谋和蓄意的</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军相信军事压力正在发挥作用，但表示哈马斯尚未被击败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</link><description>以色列高级指挥官认为，现在与哈马斯达成协议的条件更好 ■ 与此同时，内塔尼亚胡及其政府的极右翼在谈判中没有表现出更大灵活性的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利以以色列和伊朗为例，敦促共和党人团结起来支持特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</link><description>美国前驻联合国大使称赞特朗普的外交政策：“在以色列和哈马斯之间，唐纳德·特朗普很清楚谁是我们的朋友，谁是我们的敌人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉威胁称，如果以色列加强对黎巴嫩平民的打击，他们将把袭击范围扩大到以色列境内</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</link><description>以色列国防军：部队在加沙地带北部遭到袭击，以回应周二对斯德洛特的攻击 ■ 以色列国防军发言人向《阿拉伯报》表示：哈马斯领导人的顽固阻止我们达成协议 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，加沙已有 38,713 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，89,166 人受伤，哈马斯以色列卫生部表示 ■ 以色列国防军：真主党在最近的攻击中向以色列发射了 15 枚火箭弹；没有受伤或损坏</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:38:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普任命“美国第一”副总统时，犹太共和党高层坚称共和党是“唯一亲以色列的政党”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-jewish-republican-uses-gop-convention-to-make-case-for-trump-to-u-s-jews/00000190-be06-d3a7-a79e-fe57603f0000</link><description>共和党犹太联盟主席马特·布鲁克斯在共和党全国代表大会上对欢呼的人群说：“在拜登总统领导下的四年灾难性经历之后，特朗普将重建美以关系。”他告诉记者，他是共和党内部“战斗”的一部分，以“确保塔克·卡尔森党派没有立足之地”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:29:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-jewish-republican-uses-gop-convention-to-make-case-for-trump-to-u-s-jews/00000190-be06-d3a7-a79e-fe57603f0000</guid></item><item><title>监管机构猛烈抨击家庭长达数周的等待以色列社会服务部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</link><description>家庭需要等待数周甚至数月才能从社会事务部机构获得帮助，认为对孩子构成风险的父母可以与他们举行监督会议，部分原因是大多数机构的工作时间少于要求的时间</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 21:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这名以色列裔美国人质的父母在共和党大会上发言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</link><description>奥马尔·诺伊特拉（Omer Neutra）在加沙被扣为人质已有九个多月了，他们的父母罗南·诺伊特拉（Ronen Neutra）和奥纳·诺伊特拉（Orna Neutra）说，“我们有发言权，我们将与美国人民对话，并要求他们加入我们的战斗。”两人表示，他们的讲话旨在让美国人牢记人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长报道了士兵因杀害哈马斯恐怖分子而被捕后自杀的虚假故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特议员写道，“追捕我们英雄士兵的检察官办公室不是国家检察官办公室，而是敌人的检察官办公室。”一旦发现该故事是虚假的，该帖子就被删除了</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</guid></item><item><title>JD Vance 对以色列的立场如何？无论特朗普告诉他去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</link><description>任何参与其中的人都应该问自己：当万斯无人跟随时会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层，14,000名特工人员死伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</link><description>以军认为，哈马斯陷入人力危机，对战地武装力量的指挥控制能力正在削弱，武装分子和指挥官的动机出现“裂痕”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友警告称，由于财政部长斯莫特里奇在西岸的政策，西方将针对定居活动人士实施新的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</link><description>被认为相对亲以色列的戴维·拉米本周作为英国外交大臣首次访问以色列，他在与以色列领导人的所有会晤中都提出了这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 284 天：以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军袭击了近东救济工程处学校，造成 15 人死亡。以色列国防军称，恐怖分子在此活动。 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：加沙南部汗尤尼斯有 17 人死亡。枪击案 ■ 以色列人因涉嫌为伊朗工作而被捕 ■ 战争进入 284 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯关押在加沙的以色列女兵的家人发布了被囚禁第一天的新照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</link><description>照片显示，阿甘·伯杰、丹妮拉·吉尔博亚、利里·阿尔巴格、纳马·利维和卡琳娜·阿里耶夫在加沙地带的一间公寓内受伤。据军方消息人士称，这些照片是几周前在加沙地带的一次行动中发现的</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特起诉以色列人，据称该人被伊朗在网上招募从事反国家行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</link><description>21 岁的 Elimelech Stern 是以色列中部城市贝特谢梅什的居民，据称伊朗情报部门在网上联系并要求他执行悬挂横幅、藏匿金钱和运送包裹等“任务”，以换取报酬，随后被捕。加密货币支付</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</guid></item></channel></rss>